== Usage ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Open a document with a sketch containing horizontal guide lines, and optionally a target solid.
# Run the macro '''CSV2Objects.FCMacro''' from the Macro menu.
# In the task panel, choose a CSV file, encoding and delimiter.
# Scan guide lines and assign CSV columns to each active line.
# Choose a font, extrusion height, boolean mode and export format (STL/3MF/STEP).
# Use the live preview to adjust your settings.
# Press '''OK''' to generate and export the geometry for all CSV rows.
# Press '''Cancel''' to clear preview objects and close the dialog.
</div>

